.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, fanta, tea, soy-milk, mirinda
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk | lemonade | mirinda | tea     | fanta  |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat    | dog      | mouse  | guinea-pig | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, indie, punk, soul
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, april, june, october, august, september
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in june is the fan of indie##1
9. the fan of country is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | soul   | punk      | classical | blues  | country   |
| Birthday   | june | september | july | april   | august | october |

