.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, disco, dubstep, indie
City: edinburgh, colone, rome, berlin, new-york, paris
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
2. the fan of country is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person traveling to paris is the fan of disco##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | disco | blues      | classical  | indie | dubstep |
| City     | edinburgh | paris  | new-york | rome | berlin  | colone    |

