.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, ritmeester, davidoff, prince, bluemaster, tiparillo
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, electronic, house, techno
 1. the fan of disco is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the fan of country##1
 3. the fan of house is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
10. the prince-smoker is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Cigar         | prince | tiparillo | pall-mall | bluemaster | ritmeester | davidoff  |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | electronic  | disco  | classical | house      | country |

