.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, lemonade, sprite, tea, milk
There are 6 different nationalities: american, australian, brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
1. the mexican is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the american##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the australian is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the german is the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the brazilian##1
7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Beverage   | milk    | lemonade    | mirinda | tea     | 7up   | sprite     |
| Nationality   | german | australian | mexican | brazilian | chinese | american |

