.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, funk, hip-hop, punk, reggae, salsa
House: townhouse, cape-cod, gothic-revival, craftsman, art-deco, cottage
1. the fan of hip-hop is the art-deco house##1
2. the cottage house is the fan of punk##1
3. the cottage house is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
5. the cape-cod house is the fan of salsa##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
8. the cottage house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | ambient  | reggae     | hip-hop    | funk  | punk          |
| House         | cape-cod  | townhouse | gothic-revival | art-deco | craftsman | cottage |

