.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
House: townhouse, farmhouse, cape-cod, colonial, art-deco, ranch-style
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, thriller, western, zombie
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is the farmhouse house##1
4. the colonial house is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
6. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
7. the ranch-style house is the person watching family movies##1
8. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| House          | farmhouse | ranch-style   | art-deco  | cape-cod    | colonial  | townhouse |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | family | zombie | western | satire | thriller |

