.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: hiking, video-games, board-games, singing, camping, writing
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, librarian, manager, pilot, writer
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
4. the librarian is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is the manager##1
8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
9. the pilot is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Hobby   | writing    | hiking     | board-games | video-games | singing | camping   |
| Job        | writer | manager | pilot | librarian   | coach    | fisherman |

