.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
There are 6 different nationalities: british, dutch, french, indian, polish, spanish
There are 6 different favourite colors: amber, mauve, coral, pink, blood-red, emerald
1. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
2. the indian is on the left of the dutch##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the polish##1
4. the person who likes pink is the indian##1
5. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
6. the spanish is on the left of the indian##1
7. the french is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
8. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the spanish##1
9. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Nationality   | polish | spanish | indian    | dutch | french  | british |
| Color     | mauve    | blood-red | pink | emerald   | coral | amber    |

