3. the fisherman is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the fisherman##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the dressmaker##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the journalist##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the dressmaker##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |    4    |      5       |     6     |
