.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-15::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, february, may, december, october, august
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, ship, subway
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's birthday is in august##1
8. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |
| Birthday        | may     | october | february   | december      | august | april |
| Transport   | motorbike | ship  | airplane | helicopter | jet-ski   | subway     |

